title: ZBrush v3.1 + Keygen
description:
ZBrush 3.1 with KeyGen

ZBrush 3.1 is an innovative and powerful tool for digital sculpting.
Includes ZMapper and Displacement Exporter, whic allow more flexibility for exporting your sculpt.
ZBrush 3.1 also now includes Poseable Symmetry. Keep symmetry on your model at the click of a button. No matter the pose.

--------------------------------------------------------------------

See included readme for step-by-step instructions.
